                 <p>The XSLT is adapted from the old <a href="http://www.relfun.org/ruleml/rfml2ruleml.xsl">XSLT</a> Stylesheet which maps a Hornlog RFML program to an older version of RuleML rulebase.It is designed to map RFML to RuleML 0.89.</p>
